<br>
I used to summon a bunch of lev rings and keep lev up, so I can run out over the water if need be, but that is optional.<br>
<br>
Should be able pull them ok without Jboots or similar.  Level 8 bolt works a treat for getting their attention from far enough back to run to pet.  But speed makes it a bit safer.<br>
<br>
Can't comment on the rest, I came here at 49 with my new pet.  never tried 44, and so sick of these things never want to go back and test it out (I did 49-53 here, 3 AA points, and camped AC 5 or 6 times to sell the Jboots of the MQ for cash - I really couldn't handle seeing another clops).<br>
<br>
Stay away from the tainted and corrupted clops, and at 44 Quag would be a major pain.  If they engage, sick pet on them and gate/camp out. (actually, corrupted summons, so if he gets on pet, gating probably best bet).<br>
