<br>
They hit in the 70s-80s, and have about 3-4k Hit points.  With the 44 fire pet and air pet, it took quite a bit of healing to keep them in the fight.  Generally I threw about 40% of my mana into the fight.  There was no savings by chaining pets, because It took forever to shake aggro back to new pet.<br>
<br>
